&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Demonstrate a software developer mindset, building tools when necessary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Knowledge of virtualization, networking, and Linux internals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to clearly communicate your thoughts, ask the right questions, and defend your views&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
