&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Watershed Bio is hiring a Performance Marketing Analyst to integrate and own reporting for all digital marketing activity for our growth stage biocomputing platform. You will assess &amp;amp; combine data from Watershed’s digital channels (including: website visitor behavior, gated content downloads, and PPC advertising metrics). You will understand how this data translates to our sales pipeline, analyze how we can optimize marketing spend to drive business growth, and advise &amp;amp; empower leadership to make data-driven decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The right person will have a strong background in building reports and analyzing digital marketing activity across many fields. You should be a stickler for accountability and accuracy — and pride yourself on delivering actionable insights.&lt;/p&gt;
